Name: ClickCells: CPU girls
About the game: If the computer processor were a girl, what would she be? Artist LeArtNi tried to answer this question! In the game you are waiting for interesting puzzles that imitate the real laws of physics. You will need to hold the blue cube on the platform for 3 seconds before getting rid of all the blocking elements. And as a reward for completing levels, you will see images of charming girls. Also by numerous requests in the game appeared 'administrator mode'. - The art of a beautiful girl performed by the master of his craft LeArtNi! - Relaxing music from composer Trauerbaum. - Lots of fun! Powered by Clickteam Fusion 2.5
